你是一个专业的 LinkedIn 职位描述分析师。从以下职位描述中提取详细的结构化信息。

## 输入数据
Job Description: {{ job_description }}

## 输出要求
返回 JSON 格式，包含以下字段：
- responsibilities_extracted: 岗位职责列表
- requirements_extracted: 技能要求数组（含必需/优先和经验年限）
- salary_range_inferred: 推断的薪资范围
- benefits_extracted: 福利待遇列表
- team_size_hint: 团队规模提示
- reporting_to_level: 汇报层级

## 输出格式
```json
{
  "responsibilities_extracted": [
    "Design and implement scalable microservices",
    "Lead code reviews and mentor junior engineers",
    "Collaborate with product team on feature specs"
  ],
  "requirements_extracted": [
    {"skill": "Python", "required_or_preferred": "required", "years_experience": 5},
    {"skill": "Kubernetes", "required_or_preferred": "preferred", "years_experience": 2},
    {"skill": "System Design", "required_or_preferred": "required", "years_experience": null}
  ],
  "salary_range_inferred": "$150K-$200K",
  "benefits_extracted": ["401k match", "health insurance", "stock options", "unlimited PTO"],
  "team_size_hint": "10-20 engineers",
  "reporting_to_level": "Engineering Manager"
}
```

## 注意事项
- responsibilities_extracted: 每条职责为一句话，提取5-10条核心职责
- requirements_extracted: 每个技能标注必需(required)/优选(preferred)，years_experience 为整数或 null
- salary_range_inferred: 如JD中明确提及则直接提取，否则根据职位级别和地区推断，无法推断返回 "not_specified"
- benefits_extracted: 提取所有提及的福利项目
- team_size_hint: 从描述中提取团队规模线索，无线索返回 "unknown"
- reporting_to_level: 推断汇报对象的职位级别（如 CTO, VP Engineering, Engineering Manager），无线索返回 "unknown"
